videos.headline: Ehlinger tosses TD on opening drive
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds Brennan Eagles for the 7-yard untouched touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger tosses TD on opening drive) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wright's falling 38-yard catch sets up an easy WVU TD
videos.description: Jarret Doege airs out a pass to Winston Wright Jr. to set up a 12-yard touchdown run from Leddie Brown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wright's falling 38-yard catch sets up an easy WVU TD) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson hits WVU defenders with spin move, video game stiff-arm
videos.description: Bijan Robinson puts a WVU defender in a spin cycle and stiff arms another to break free, but the refs call him out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson hits WVU defenders with spin move, video game stiff-arm) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Esdale rocks the baby after huge catch
videos.description: WVU wide receiver Isaiah Esdale leaps above a Texas defender to make the 28-yard grab.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Esdale rocks the baby after huge catch) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Did West Virginia's QB just throw two completions on the same play?
videos.description: WVU's Jarret Doege gets his first pass attempt batted by a Texas defender, but he catches the deflection and tries to throw forward again but is called for the penalty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Did West Virginia's QB just throw two completions on the same play?) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger goes deep to Smith for the go-ahead TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger launches a 33-yard touchdown pass to Jake Smith to give Texas the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger goes deep to Smith for the go-ahead TD) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: WVU coach irate over potential missed P.I. call
videos.description: WVU coach Neal Brown isn't happy on the sidelines as Texas comes up with a huge stop.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (WVU coach irate over potential missed P.I. call) 2020/11/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger's TDs and Texas' defense lifts them over WVU
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger tosses two touchdowns and throws for 184 yards, while Texas' defense makes big plays to lead the Longhorns to their third straight win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ehlinger's TDs and Texas' defense lifts them over WVU) 2020/11/7 ESHEET SOTFULL
